Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.21,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fade(501,0)\t(0,0,\fscx120,\fscy120)\pos(960,707)}Matsumoto Gets Angry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there are times when I get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot.\N- Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was driving. There was this narrow road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't even want \Nto go that way, but I had to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An older lady and a kid were walking there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid was dragging a toy behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The lady looked at it as if \Nit was cute or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What were they thinking!\N- Well, maybe they just didn't notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't notice me at \Nall! So here's the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do, as the \Nperson behind the wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Honk the horn.\N- Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too loud.\N- That was a good answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:01:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I did so. I did it as soft as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, horns are always loud. \NIt's not about how soft you press it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the length of the honk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So the lady was eyeing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she had a face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like "Give me a break,\Nthis isn't a walkway".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm an adult, I don't get mad over \Nthat like I would have in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I rolled down the window and asked "What?".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The lady screamed "You startled the kid!".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened next?\NI was still talking to the lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:02:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I don't know where the hell he came from, an old man with a huge dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just because you're a TV personality, you think you can get away with anything?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I did it just because I'm on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you were following \Nthem and did it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So she was saying "You startled the kid!".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But the kid and the big dog were like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not startled in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, suppose they were, even though \N that was so totally not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is so bad about startling a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:03:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it wrong to startle a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To raise a kid in this world\N without startling is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To reach adulthood without the sound\N of a honking horn is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"What am I going to do? What's a horn?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"What's a horn?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I'm driving, and the driver in front\N of me doesn't notice the green light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Damn I want to honk the \N horn, damn I want to!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"But what if there's a kid in\N that car. I can't startle him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm picking up a friend.\N But he doesn't notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"I should sound the horn. But\N wait, maybe there's a kid here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can't startle a kid, you know!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to live like that!

